I'm not familiar enough with `nosetests` to provide help here. From the stacktrace it seems that somehow the use of `nosetests` is resulting in an incorrect import of TensorFlow where it is looking for the `decorated` symbol in the wrong module.

Marking as "Community Support" since I don't believe anyone on the team here has the expertise to debug interactions with `nosetests`.
